<view class="page" wx:if="{{!loading}}">
  <view class="banner">
    <text class="banner-title">{{title}}</text>
    <text class="banner-sub">请勾选实际到场的付费球友，系统将按实际到场人数重新均摊场地费，多退少补。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-head">付费报名球友（{{payList.length}} 人）</view>
    <view class="empty" wx:if="{{payList.length === 0}}">本局暂无付费报名球友，无需结算。</view>
    <view class="member {{item.attended ? 'on' : ''}}" wx:for="{{payList}}" wx:key="userId" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="onToggle">
      <image class="avatar" src="{{item.avatar || '/assets/icons/profile.png'}}" mode="aspectFill" />
      <view class="m-info">
        <text class="m-name">{{item.name}}</text>
        <text class="m-paid">已付 ¥{{item.paidYuan}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="check {{item.attended ? 'checked' : ''}}">{{item.attended ? '到场' : '缺席'}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 发起人本人是否到场 -->
  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-head">我本人是否到场打球</view>
    <view class="member organizer {{organizerAttended ? 'on' : ''}}" bindtap="onToggleOrganizer">
      <view class="m-info">
        <text class="m-name">{{organizerName}}</text>
        <text class="m-paid">{{organizerAttended ? '到场则与球友一同分摊场地费' : '未到场则不分摊场地费'}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="check {{organizerAttended ? 'checked' : ''}}">{{organizerAttended ? '我到场' : '我没来'}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card summary" wx:if="{{payList.length > 0}}">
    <view class="sum-row"><text>场地费总额</text><text class="val">¥{{totalFeeYuan}}</text></view>
    <view class="sum-row"><text>到场球友</text><text class="val">{{attendedCount}} 人</text></view>
    <view class="sum-row"><text>分摊总人数{{organizerAttended ? '（含我）' : ''}}</text><text class="val">{{divisor}} 人</text></view>
    <view class="sum-row hl"><text>重算后人均</text><text class="val">¥{{perPersonYuan}}</text></view>
    <view class="sum-row" wx:if="{{organizerAttended}}"><text>我应分摊（自付）</text><text class="val">¥{{organizerShareYuan}}</text></view>
    <view class="sum-row hl"><text>结算到我的零钱</text><text class="val">¥{{settleToMeYuan}}</text></view>
    <view class="divider"></view>
    <view class="preview-item" wx:for="{{preview}}" wx:key="userId">
      <text class="p-name">{{item.name}}</text>
      <text class="p-act {{item.type}}">{{item.text}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tips">
    <text>· 到场者多付的部分将原路退回微信；少付的部分将生成待补缴账单。</text>
    <text>· 缺席（爽约）者已付费用不退还，并将扣除信用分。</text>
    <text>· 若您本人到场，将与球友一同分摊场地费，您那一份自动从结算金额中扣除。</text>
    <text>· 扣除您自付份额与退款后，余额结算到您（发起人）的微信零钱。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <button class="btn-primary" loading="{{submitting}}" bindtap="onSubmit">确认结算</button>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="loading" wx:else>加载中...</view>
